统计，全年完成生产总值</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">70</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元以上，增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16.82%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；完成全社会固定资产投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">48</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">48.56%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；完成地方一般预算收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.17</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4300</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">24.71%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；完成规模工业增加值</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">31.08%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；农民人均纯收入达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5800</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">520</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（一）工业经济快速发展，招商引资成效显著。加快了工业园区建设，筹措资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元，实施了园区二路南段延伸工程以及园区配套设施工程，新开工建设了联乐工业园、嘉能热电、中能锂电、湖北山树风建材等投资过亿元的项目，园区经济占全县规模工业的比重达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">60%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。通过采取县财政借资建设、企业投产后税收抵扣的办法，积极支持各镇规划建设镇级工业园，在全县形成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一区多园</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的发展格局。坚持因企施策，多管齐下，加大了对企业扶持服务力度，重点在煤、电、油、运和劳动用工等方面加强了调度。加快了企业技术改造步伐，纺织、钢管、船舶制造等行业产能大幅提升。全县规模企业净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，发展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">125</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，入库税金首次突破</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">进一步完善了招商引资奖励办法，聘请了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">26</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">名外来客商为招商代理人，组团赴广东、浙江、武汉等地参加招商推介活动，全年新签合同项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">46</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，其中投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，合同引进资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">46.2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，实际到位资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">19.3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元。加快了重点项目建设进程，全县续建、新建投资过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元项目有</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">33</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，已建成投产的有</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，这些续建、新建项目成为拉动我县工业经济快速增长的新亮点，特别是葛洲坝水泥项目的建成投产，实现了我县在引进国内</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">强企业上零的突破。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（二）特色农业稳步发展，新农村建设进程加快。严格落实各项惠农政策，全年共发放各种涉农政策性补贴资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3439</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。建成了两个万亩以上省级水稻优质高产示范片，粮食种植面积和总产量分别比上年增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">与</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；生猪出栏、家禽出笼分别增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.3%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；油菜生产实现恢复性增长。引进了湖北大禾公司投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，规划建设</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩现代设施农业基地，已建成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">200</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩。大力推进蔬菜标准化生产，继续推行蔬菜质量安全检测周报制度，全年产地蔬菜抽检合格率达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，潘家湾蔬菜基地被列入全省有机蔬菜种植基地。全县新建水产健康养殖小区</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，名特优水产品比重提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上。着力推进了农业产业化，重点抓好洪发水产、国美食品、绿丰蔬菜等企业扩大生产，全县新增省级农业产业化龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，农副产品加工企业发展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">54</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。加快发展林特经济，全县森林覆盖率达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25.8%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，我县被省绿化委授予</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">湖北省绿化模范县</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">荣誉称号。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">在新农村建设上，坚持规划先行，完成了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">57</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个行政村的新农村建设规划编制；以官桥八组为示范，以花口村、护县洲村、肖家洲村、余码头村、大牛山村等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">11</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个示范村为重点，采取政府引导、村民自主、对口帮扶等形式，组织开展了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">百企联百村、共建新农村</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">百里文明走廊、万户清洁家园</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和村庄整治</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">百日大会战</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">等活动，对城乡干道沿线村的卫生环境进行了集中整治。坚持项目带动，重点实施了三湖连江灌区续建配套、农村安全饮水、土地整理、一建三改等工程，累计开工项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">290</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多个，竣工项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">150</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多个，完成投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿多元，农村面貌和农业生产条件明显改善。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（三）基础设施明显改善，旅游发展风生水起。深入开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">委县合作</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">办县对接</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">局县会商</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">等活动，全年共向上争取项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">55</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，争取上级补助资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，一批重大基础项目建设进程明显加快。全面完成了京珠连接线、嘉赤线茶石段翻修和高铁至陆溪二级公路改造一期工程；新建了葛洲坝水泥专用码头，改造了潘家湾深水码头，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元的武嘉一级公路改造项目、投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的陆口大桥项目进展顺利，尤其是我县被列入武汉新港建设规划，为嘉鱼县未来发展开拓了新空间。投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元全面完成了茶庵新区主干道和三湖连江景观路刷黑工程，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元实施了三湖桥建设，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元完成了环三湖连江污水截流工程和茶庵新区污水收集管道工程建设，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的北京桑德污水处理项目已完成厂区主体工程。专项投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">150</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，对县城区道街路巷、居民小区的楼栋门牌、地名标识进行了全面清理和规范设置，对城区公共部分、单位庭院和主干道两旁进行了绿化改造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">省级园林城市通过了省考核验收。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">围绕建设旅游新县目标，组织专班对全县旅游资源进行了摸底调查，科学编制了全县旅游产业发展规划；扶持发展了一批有规模、上档次的庭院经济和设施农业，努力形成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一路、一景、一林、一果、一批农家乐</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的发展格局。特别是一期投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元的山湖温泉项目于去年</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">月</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">日建成营业，年接待游客可达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">70</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人次，极大地拉动了我县餐饮、旅游等相关产业的发展。据初步统计，全年实现旅游综合收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2200</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">40%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（四）商贸流通繁荣活跃，财税金融平稳运行。大力发展专业市场，建成了南嘉农产品批发市场。继续推进了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万村千乡</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">市场工程，镇、村农资店和农家店建设有了新进展。加快发展农村消费市场，完成了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">67</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家家电销售网点备案登记工作，全年落实家电和汽车下乡补贴资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">270</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。进一步规范了市场经营秩序，重点抓好了放心菜、放心肉工程，全社会消费品零售总额达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">19.29</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20.8%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。全年完成外贸出口创汇</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">340</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万美元，实际利用外资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">483</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万美元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">过去的一年，全县实现财政总收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">26%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；加大了对社会保障和就业、医疗卫生、环境保护等方面的重点支出，保证了社会稳定支出、政策性支出和重点建设支出，确保了全县各项工作正常运转。全县金融机构年末各项存款余额</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">33.87</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比年初增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5.6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元；各项贷款余额</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">21.76</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比年初增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.85</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（五）各项事业协调发展，和谐社会稳步推进。积极向上争取低保救助及移民后期扶持资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5439</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，全面落实了各项优扶救助政策，全县纳入城镇低保</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">11144</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，实现了动态管理下的应保尽保；农村低保达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10532</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，保障标准逐步提高；大病救助</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1020</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，救助资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">501</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。全县五项社会保险扩面新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7361</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，征收保险费</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.21</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元。农村合作医疗参合农民</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">24.13</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人，参合率达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">85%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，发放补偿金额</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1931.2 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。加快了安居工程建设，全县累计发放廉租住房补贴</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">145</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">196</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">户困难户通过摇号住进了经济适用房。创新利益导向机制，开展了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">南嘉惠民计生阳光行动</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，落实了计划生育</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一证管多证</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">制度，加大了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两非</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">案件查处力度，稳定了全县低生育水平。认真做好了甲型流感、手足口病、血吸虫病等传染病防控工作。加大了食品药品市场监督管理，进一步巩固了国家级食品安全示范县创建成果。率先在全市完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">普九</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">债务化解，全面落实了义务教育阶段教师绩效工资，全县高考、中考成绩综合评比均获全市第一，我县被评为咸宁市中高考和备考先进单位。加快了科技兴农、科技兴工步伐，向上争取资金并组织实施了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个科技项目。加大了文体设施建设力度，县文体中心顺利建成，新建文化站</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、农家书屋</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，建成新农村体育场地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">13</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">处，成功举办了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">歌唱祖国</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&middot;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">唱响嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">庆祝建国六十周年大型广场红歌大家唱活动，极大地丰富了人民群众的文娱生活。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">深入开展了平安创建，严厉打击黑社会性质、邪教组织、黄赌毒等各类犯罪活动，全年共摧毁各类犯罪团伙</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">41</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，破获各类刑事案件</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">432</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">起，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">起现发命案全部及时侦破；落实了综合治理措施，组建了县维稳中心和镇综治维稳中心，在全县构建起</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四位一体</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">治安防范网络，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2009</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，我县被评为全国平安县。大力推行了领导干部</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四访促和谐</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和信访领导小组例会制度，依法妥善解决了一批信访积案、难案和缠访案件。强化了安全生产工作责任，安全生产事故发生次数、致伤人数、直接经济损失大幅下降。与此同时，国防动员、民兵预备役和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">双拥</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">工作得到加强，对台外事、民族宗教、人防、气象等工作扎实推进，人事编制、统计物价、审计监察、档案方志等工作取得新的成绩，妇女、儿童、老龄、残疾人等事业全面发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（六）自身建设不断加强，政府形象得到提升。深入开展学习实践科学发展观和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">作风建设年</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">活动，政务环境进一步改善。加强了政府系统党风廉政建设，源头治腐力度加大，进一步完善了国库集中支付制度，拓宽了政府采购领域，严格执行了招投标制度，加大了对国家扩大内需项目监督检查力度。加强了行政服务网络建设和政务公开工作，完善了政府科学民主决策机制，健全了应急救援和减灾防灾体系，普法教育和依法行政工作有序推进。自觉接受人大法律监督和政协民主监督，高度重视并认真办理了风华化工、嘉能热电搬迁和在武嘉沿线建立农副产品交易市场等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件议案，目前风华化工和嘉能热电搬迁已制定了方案，厂地选址、征地等工作已完成，基础工程已开工建设；筹措资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">700</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元，已完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">14</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个交易市场的土方工程。全年办理人大代表建议</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">48</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件，办理政协委员提案</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">72</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件，见面率与回复率均达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年初承诺为民办好的八件实事基本完成。一是全年新增就业岗位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，帮助下岗失业人员和困难人员再就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，转移农民工就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8907</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，组织城镇下岗失业人员和农民工各类技能培训</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4006</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次。二是金水河流域综合整治工程已列入国家财政补贴投资计划。三是积极筹措资金，解决了牌洲湾、潘家湾、官桥等镇</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万农村人口安全饮水问题。四是启动了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万平米廉租住房建设，已完成三通一平、基础勘探、建筑设计等前期工作。五是争取项目资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1800</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">多万元，实施了中小学校舍改造项目。六是县人民医院改扩建工程目前已完成了征地、土地补偿、地质勘探、场地平整等前期工作。七是城区视频监控系统一期工程已完成招投标，正在进行栽杆施工。八是完成了北门湖红珠港排污工程建设，改善了附近居民生活环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表，过去的一年，我们坚持以科学发展观为指导，做到各项工作高起点部署，快节奏推进，高标准完成。一年来，我们坚持在改革创新中前进，在真抓实干中发展，在重重困难中与全县人民风雨同行，全县经济社会各方面都发生了新的重大变化。这些成绩的取得，是县委正确领导的结果，是县人大、县政协监督支持的结果，是全县上下奋力拼搏的结果。在此，我谨代表县人民政府，向全县广大干部群众，向各位人大代表、政协委员，向全县离退休老领导、老同志，向全体武警战士、消防官兵和政法干警，向所有关心支持嘉鱼发展的社会各界朋友，表示衷心的感谢，并致以崇高的敬意！</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表，回顾过去一年的工作，我们也清醒地认识到，全县经济社会发展中还存在一些困难和问题：一是与发展较快的兄弟县市区相比，县域经济总量仍然偏小；二是农业产业化发展滞后，工业支撑力不强，现代服务业依然缺乏；三是供水供电保障能力差，城市管理执法力度弱，失地农民生活保障低；四是行政效能需要进一步提高，政府部门少数工作人员作风不够实，服务意识不强。对这些困难和问题，我们将高度重视，采取有效措施，认真加以解决。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">二、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年政府工作安排</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">今年是执行</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">规划的收尾之年，是做好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">规划开局准备的基础之年，也是我县抢抓机遇、大干快干的关键之年。做好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年政府工作，责任重大，意义深远。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年政府工作的总体要求是：坚持以邓小平理论和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三个代表</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">重要思想为指导，深入学习实践科学发展观，认真贯彻落实党的十七大和十七届四中全会精神以及中央和省市经济工作会议精神，抢抓机遇，乘势而上，推进全县经济社会加快发展，全面实现</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">规划目标，努力建设农业强县、工业大县、旅游新县。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年全县经济社会发展的主要预期目标是</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五增两降三突破</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">：即生产总值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，地方一般预算收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，社会消费品零售总额增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，规模工业增加值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，农民人均纯收入增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">600</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元以上；万元生产总值综合能耗下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，出生人口性别比下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个百分点；全社会固定资产投资突破</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，直接利用外资和外贸出口均突破</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万美元。同时，污染物总量排放减少</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，城镇居民人均可支配收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，城镇新增就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，五项保险新增扩面</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，人口自然增长率控制在</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6&permil;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以内，城镇人口登记失业率控制在</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以内，森林覆盖率达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">26.8%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，城镇化水平达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">55%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">围绕今年的目标任务，我们将着力抓好以下七个方面的工作：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（一）以新型工业化为主攻方向，提升工业经济发展水平</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">进一步强化工业主导地位，着力提升经济发展水平，加快工业大县建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">打造园区平台，加快招商引资。全面完成园区一路、二路延伸工程，形成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两纵两横</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大园区框架。加快推进开发区新征土地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">七通一平</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工程建设，力争开发区新增规模企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，园区经济占规模工业比重达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">65%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。继续加大对镇级工业园的扶持力度，加快完善</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一区多园</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">发展格局，各镇工业园新落户项目要达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上。掀起新一轮招商引资热潮，严格落实招商引资奖励政策，继续推行全民招商、专班招商、以商招商和活动招商等行之有效的招商方式，重点引进一批与我县优势产业关联度高的现代制造业、现代农业和新兴产业项目，延伸产业链条，扩大产业规模，真正形成引进一个、带来一群、开发一片的集群效应。力争全年新引进中国</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">强企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，实际到位资金超过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">坚持项目带动，做强优势产业。围绕抓好申邦化纤、洁丽雅纺织二期扩建、盛宇染织三期扩建等项目建设，壮大纺织产业规模；抓好山树风建材、金嘉木业等项目建设，壮大森工建材产业；抓好中能锂电、风华化工</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;1830&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">工程、嘉能热电整体迁建等项目建设，改造提升化工能源产业；抓好利口福食品、康师傅方便面脱水菜项目建设，扶持洪发水产、绿丰食品等企业做大做强，壮大农副产品加工业；争取将钢管制造业纳入全省重点成长型产业集群。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强自主创新，推进节能减排。完善企业自主创新机制，加强信息技术推广应用，提高工业信息化水平。加快发展高新技术产业，着力培育新能源、新材料、电子信息、生物医药等新兴战略产业，力争新增高新技术企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。进一步强化举措，推进节能减排，发展循环经济，引导企业做好工业废物综合利用和再生资源循环利用工作，严格实行工业废水达标排放，力争今年实现削减化学需氧量</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">432</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万吨、二氧化硫排放量</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">44</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">吨，全县万元生产总值能耗下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（二）以发展现代农业为目标，扎实做好农业农村工作</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">进一步发挥特色农业优势，优化农业结构，扩大规模经营，拓宽农民增收渠道，巩固和发展农业农村好形势。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力发展现代高效农业。立足蔬菜、水产特色优势，加快发展设施农业、生态农业、订单农业、创汇农业和观光农业。大力推进蔬菜、水产、优质粮油、林特、畜禽等特色农产品基地建设，推进农产品规模化和区域化生产，提高农产品基地建设水平。以创建蔬菜标准化生产示范县为契机，新扩建蔬菜大棚面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩，重点抓好阴山大禾设施农业基地建设。以争创全省水产大县为契机，加强水产板块核心区建设，特色渔业比重提高</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上。以争创全国绿化模范县为契机，巩固全省绿化模范县创建成果，重点抓好官桥镇优质油茶基地建设，抓好高铁镇、渡普镇有机水果基地建设，全县完成人工造林面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，新增苗木基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩，新发展优质油茶基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩。以发展养殖小区为突破口，加快珍湖、密泉湖、西凉湖、蜀湖等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个水禽养殖小区建设，力争水禽养殖规模达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万羽。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力推进农业产业化建设。抢抓省委、省政府实施农产品加工</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四个一批</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工程机遇，重点依托农业主导产业和资源优势，充分利用湖北大禾、洪发水产、山绿食品、绿丰食品等农业产业化龙头企业的良好基础和带动功能，加速发展一批经济实力强、投资规模大、市场前景好、可持续发展的新型农产品加工龙头企业。加快发展外向型农业，扩大农产品出口备案基地规模，力争蔬菜、水产品年加工量达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万吨以上，农产品出口创汇</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万美元以上。着力培育现代农业经营主体，新增省级龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，全县省级龙头企业总数达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，培育市级以上休闲观光农业示范单位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。进一步推进县农产品质量安全监督检验站规范化建设，建立完善蔬菜市场准入机制和产地准出制度。加快推进蔬菜标准化生产，大力支持和引导农业专业合作社发展和规范化运行，开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">嘉鱼蔬菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">地理标志申报和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">贴标工作，加快申报绿色有机食品品牌，力争实现有机食品品牌零的突破。加快制定优惠政策，积极引导和鼓励社会力量投资建设蔬菜交易市场。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">进一步加快新农村建设。以武嘉线、咸潘线、嘉泉线为重点，选择一部分村组作为全县第二批新农村建设示范点，在农村安全饮水、小型水库除险加固、土地整理、双低改造、小流域治理、一建三改等方面给予项目倾斜。充分发挥官桥八组的示范带动作用，探索整村推进、产业先行模式，力争通过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2-3</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年的努力，把官桥村建设成为全省新农村建设的典范。加快完善新农村建设帮扶机制，建立检查评比长效机制，推动全县新农村建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（三）以旅游产业为龙头，推动第三产业快速发展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快旅游新县建设步伐，重点发展特色旅游产业，带动商贸流通相关产业发展，全面促进投资增长，不断扩大消费需求，推动第三产业快速发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快发展旅游产业。科学制定旅游规划，尽快编制全县旅游发展总体规划和三湖连江风景区发展详细规划，推进旅游产业健康发展。强化旅游招商引资，出台加快旅游产业发展的优惠政策，力争新引进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家投资过亿元的旅游项目落户嘉鱼。统筹三湖连江山水资源开发，加快三湖连江主题公园和假日休闲、水上游乐、湖上观光、农家风情等方面的项目建设，进一步改善三湖连江风景区旅游环境。注重点线结合，继续扶持在武嘉、咸潘、嘉泉沿线发展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">农家乐</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。逐年恢复建设岳公亭、南如寺等历史文化古迹，发掘陆溪三国文化内涵，着力发展历史文化旅游。规范旅游管理，积极开展宾馆创</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">星</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">、景区创</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;A&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">、导游创佳及旅游产品推广等活动，做好旅游名镇、名村申报和山湖温泉创</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;4A&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">景区工作，加快与省内外、市内外城市旅游线路的融合，形成县内小环线、县外大环线以及周边多点连线的旅游格局，力争今年旅游综合收入比上年翻一番。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力发展商贸流通业。加快构建安全、便捷、畅通、高效的商贸流通体系，合理布局商业网点，引导网络向农村延伸，形成大市场、大流通格局。大力发展现代服务业和连锁经营、特许经营、物流配送等新型经营形式，继续开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万村千乡</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">市场工程，力争村级规范化农家店覆盖率达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。进一步加大市场秩序整治力度，重点加强蔬菜、建材、小商品批发等专业市场管理。加强南嘉农产品批发市场和现代商业城的基础设施配套建设，加快商贸流通业招商引资力度，着力打造综合性、高档次的商业中心。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">促进投资消费持续增长。抢抓中央扩大内需政策机遇，充分利用好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">委县合作</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">办县对接</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">等平台，认真研究中央经济工作会议精神，吃准国家投资政策，围绕结构调整、民生工程、社会事业、节能减排、三农等重点领域，积极策划包装和储备一批项目，扎实做好项目前期工作，抓住有利时机，积极上报争取，力争有更多项目挤进国家年度计划盘子，今年力争向上争取项目资金超过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元。进一步改善消费环境，加大价格调控和质量监管力度，严厉打击损害消费者权益行为。认真落实家电下乡、汽车下乡政策，继续做好家电、汽车下乡财政补贴工作，激活农村消费市场，改善农民生活质量。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（四）以沿江开发为重点，努力提高县域经济外向度</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">今后几年，是省委、省政府加快推进长江经济带新一轮开放开发和武汉新港建设的重要时期。我们要充分开发和利用好沿江资源，加快沿江开发步伐，建设大港口、发展大物流，进一步扩大对外开放，加快临港新城建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快完善沿江开发规划。加强与省直有关部门的沟通与衔接，组织专家对《嘉鱼县长江经济带开放开发总体规划》、《武汉新港嘉鱼港</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010-2020</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年总体规划》进行完善，科学制定武汉新港嘉鱼港空间发展、产业发展、集疏运网络和临港新城建设等专项规划，统筹规划岸线开发、基础设施、产业布局和环境保护，最大限度地发挥沿江经济效益、社会效益和生态效益。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快推进临港新城建设。立足嘉鱼的区位优势，找准发展定位，积极争取国家投资、鼓励社会融资，采取社会化、市场化运作方式，加快推进嘉鱼现有码头改造升级，重点抓好潘家湾核电重件码头、潘家湾深水码头二期工程、中港码头、方圆船舶配套码头建设。力争通过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2-3</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年努力，建成现代化装卸、集疏运于一体的沿江码头群。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快发展沿江配套产业。以做大做强船舶工业为突破口，发挥</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">办县对接</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">平台优势，争取将方圆船舶列入武船集团生产基地，新引进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家船舶制造企业落户嘉鱼，提高全县船舶工业集聚度和竞争力。突破性发展港区物流业，按照市场导向、政府推进、企业运作的方式，抓好现代物流基地、物流产业园、配送中心网络建设，重点规划建设好潘家湾物流产业园，努力将其建成鄂南地区沿江最大的物流基地。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（五）以开源节流为手段，充分发挥财税金融支撑作用</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">牢固树立综合财政、效益财政理念，抓好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">生财、聚财、理财、争财</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">工作，改进金融服务环境，最大限度地提高财税金融服务经济社会发展能力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">拓宽财源渠道，提高税收质量。综合运用税收、预算、国债、财政贴息、转移支付等手段，从产品开发、技改扩能、创新创牌等方面支持现代制造业、高新技术产业、农业产业化龙头企业和工业园区的发展，巩固支柱财源，壮大新兴财源，培育后续财源，力争明年工业税收净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，土地收益达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿以上。逐步改善财政收入结构，千方百计增加可用财力，确保全年财政一般预算收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，税收占一般预算收入的比重达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">63.2%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，比上年增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7.4</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个百分点，力争在提高财政收入质量上实现新突破。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强收支管理，做到科学理财。加强非税收入征管，强化国有资产监管，增强政府调控能力。积极争取上级专项补助资金，缓解县镇财政运转困难。继续深化部门预算、国库集中支付制度改革。完善政府采购制度，强化财政支出管理，加强财政监督，重点加强对惠农扶农、义务教育、新型农村合作医疗、扩大内需等方面的专项资金检查，进一步规范财经秩序，做到聚财有道、理财有方、用财有节，切实提高财政资金使用效益。大幅压缩公务接待费用，牢固树立过紧日子的思想，今年非政策性项目支出一律在去年基础上压缩</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">优化金融服务，促进银企共赢。充分发挥城投公司、中小企业担保公司的职能作用，全方位、多领域搭建融资平台。巩固最佳金融信用县创建成果，推进企业信用制度建设，完善中小企业贷款风险补偿机制和银企需求信息传导机制，促进银企项目对接，引导金融机构增加有效信贷投放，推进银企合作，解决企业融资难题，落实信贷激励政策，力争新增授信评级企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，新增工业贷款</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元，为全县经济社会发展提供更大支持。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（六）以基础设施建设为主体，统筹城乡协调发展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快基础设施建设，坚持在理念上有新定位，建设上有新突破，管理上有新举措，提高城乡协调发展水平。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">打造宜居家园。继续巩固省级园林城市、省级文明县城创建成果，通过加快构建道路网络、兴建公园游园、建设垃圾处理厂等设施，完善城区功能，提升城市品位，为争创国家级园林城市打下良好基础。完善城区基础设施建设，完成新区污水收集提升泵站及管网建设，完成北门湖污水提升泵站改造及配套管网建设，建设改造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个提升泵站和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3500</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">米污水收集主管网。完成嘉能热电、风华化工、兴宁化工等企业的整体迁建，进一步净化城区环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快交通建设。重点抓好县城至赤壁镇沿江一级公路、嘉鱼至武汉沿江高速公路、嘉鱼港等项目的申报，积极争取京广铁路复线、潘家湾至京广线铁路等项目纳入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">规划。认真做好嘉鱼长江大桥及连线高速项目前期准备工作，全力服务咸潘一级公路建设。同时，要加强对在建基础项目质量的管理，严禁出现</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">豆腐渣</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">工程。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">提高城乡管理水平。加强小城镇建设管理，顺应农村人口、村庄数量逐步减少的趋势，合理确定中心村数量和布点，通过科学规划引导农村人口向中心城镇转移，为产业发展和民间创业提供空间。强化城管执法手段，不断提升城市管理水平，特别是针对城区违法违规建设行为有所抬头的现实问题，要采取强有力的措施，依法依规坚决拆违控违，维护广大市民的切身利益。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（七）以民生保障为根本，不断提高人民群众生活水平</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">进一步强化社会保障，繁荣社会事业，维护社会秩序，真正让人民群众在改革中获得更多机遇，在发展中得到更多实惠，在稳定中共享和谐。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">不断完善社会保障体系。加快健全社会保障体系，重点抓好医疗保险扩面征缴、医疗卫生体制改革、新型农村养老保险试点、村主职干部和失地农民基本养老保险等工作。进一步搞好城镇居民最低生活保障工作，加快二期廉租房和经济适用房建设。进一步扩大社会保险覆盖面，全年新增扩面</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，城镇居民参保率达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">90%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上。拓宽创业渠道，鼓励和扶持大中专院校毕业生、返乡农民工、复员转业军人等群体自主创业；继续开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">春风送岗位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">活动，定期举办各类就业招聘会，为农民工提供更多的就业岗位。整合职业教育资源，实施阳光工程，加强农民工技能培训。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快社会事业发展。优先发展教育事业，优化教师队伍结构，加快推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两个基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">建设，促进教育均衡发展。积极推进文化大繁荣大发展，着手打造城区文化体育场馆</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">精品工程</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。挖掘嘉鱼鱼文化、三国文化，形成具有嘉鱼特色的文化品牌，借此推进文化产业的形成和发展。加快发展卫生事业，逐步建立覆盖城乡、人人享有的基本医疗卫生保健体系，加强重大疾病防控、卫生监督和妇幼保健工作，完善卫生应急体系，加快推进县人民医院整体搬迁工程建设。继续稳定低生育水平，提高符合政策生育率，综合治理出生人口性别比，强化计生服务，争创全国计生优质服务先进县。扎实推进精神文明建设，加强和改进未成年人思想道德建设，大力弘扬时代精神和文明新风。加强国防教育，推进民兵预备役和人民防空建设，进一步做好双拥、优抚安置等工作。扎实做好全国第六次人口普查工作，注重发展残疾人事业，支持妇女、儿童、老龄事业发展，扎实做好民族宗教、外事侨务、档案方志等工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">做好安全维稳工作。进一步落实安全监管和企业安全生产的主体责任，加强重点领域、重点行业的安全管理，开展隐患排查和安全生产专项整治活动，坚决杜绝重特大安全事故发生。巩固平安嘉鱼建设成果，进一步完善治安防控体系，严厉打击违法犯罪活动，不断增强人民群众的安全感。充分发挥县、镇综治维稳中心的作用，完善矛盾纠纷排查调处机制和司法救助机制，设立司法救助基金，提高化解社会不安定因素的能力。全面落实信访工作责任制和责任追究制，加大对缠访、闹访行为的打击力度，规范信访秩序。加强应急管理体系建设，不断提高应急管理工作水平。进一步整顿和规范市场经济秩序，加强食品安全监管，深化农村药品</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两网</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">三、加强政府自身建设</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">我们要牢固树立</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">发展重于一切、创业先于一切、为民高于一切</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">行政理念，不断加强政府自身建设，努力建设服务型政府。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（一）坚持改革创新，科学履行职责。根据中央、省、市的统一部署，稳步实施政府机构改革，稳妥推进行政管理体制创新，整合部门职能，规范机构设置，理顺职责关系。以新一轮政府机构改革为契机，加快职能转变，把打造服务型政府贯穿政府工作的全过程，重点做好对企业、对项目的服务工作。继续深化行政审批制度改革，进一步精简审批事项，简化办事程序。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（二）坚持依法行政，规范权力运行。主动接受县人大法律监督，自觉接受县政协民主监督，高度重视社会公众监督和新闻舆论监督，认真办理人大代表议案、建议和政协委员提案、意见。健全重大事项集体决策、专家咨询、决策评估、社会公示与听证等制度，推进行政决策的科学化、民主化。加强行政复议工作，完善行政执法责任制，规范执法行为。加强电子政务建设，加强政府门户网站建设，扩大政府信息公开，提高政务透明度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（三）坚持求真务实，优化发展环境。大力弘扬求真务实的作风，完善调查研究和现场办公制度，少坐机关多下基层，少听汇报多跑现场。大力弘扬勤政为民的作风，完善服务承诺制度和责任追究制度。大力弘扬雷厉风行的作风，推行</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工作成果倒逼法</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，以目标倒逼进度、时间倒逼部门、下级倒逼上级、督查倒逼落实。加大作风整顿力度，着力解决好少数干部职工不尽职责、不讲效率、不守纪律等问题。全面推行部门承诺服务和专班跟踪服务，开展保姆式、全程代理式服务；进一步规范行政服务中心运作机制，严格落实</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一站式</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">办公、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一条龙</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">服务和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一个窗口</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">收费的联合办公制度。同时，从整治部门</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三乱</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">入手，积极开展对干扰企业生产经营秩序行为的专项整治行动，进一步加大对损害经济发展环境行为的查处打击力度，对破坏投资环境的行为，不仅要严肃处理，还要通过电视媒体进行曝光，形成震慑效应，不断优化发展软环境。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（四）坚持廉洁从政，加强政风建设。深入推进纠风专项治理，切实纠正行业不正之风，做到以良好的政风带行风、促民风。进一步规范政府投资、政府采购、工程招投标、土地使用权交易等行为，加大重点领域、重大工程、重要环节的审计监督和行政监察力度，严肃查处违纪违法案件。认真落实党风廉政建设责任制，建立健全预防和惩治腐败长效机制，教育引导广大干部自觉增强自律意识，全力塑造廉洁勤政的政府形象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表，坚持为全县人民谋福祉，是县政府工作的出发点和落脚点。今年，我们将为全县人民办好八件实事：</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快城区自来水管网改造步伐，强化政府监管手段，坚决解决城区供水保障能力差的问题；加大投入，再解决</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.86</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万农村人口安全饮水问题，全面完成农村安全饮水</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">规划任务。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">全年新增就业岗位</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，帮助下岗失业人员和困难人员再就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，转移农民工就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人以上，组织城镇下岗失业人员和农民工技能培训</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6100</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">人次。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快武嘉一级公路和陆口大桥建设，确保今年建成通车。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">新建二乔公园。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">启动建设大道建设。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑥</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">启动沿湖景观带工程。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑦</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">实施樱花路南段延伸工程。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑧</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加强城区建房管理，加大拆违控违力度，规范城区建房秩序。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">各位代表，新的一年，农业强县要有新突破，工业大县要有新发展，旅游新县要有新局面，临港新城要有新气象，我们必须牢牢抓住发展第一要务不动摇，以推动县域经济争先进位为己任，在县委的坚强领导下，在县人大、县政协的监督支持下，团结全县人民，以更加宽广的视野谋划发展，以更加昂扬的斗志迎接挑战，以更加务实的作风勤勉做事，加快把嘉鱼建设成为咸宁市的农业示范区、工业增长极、旅游目的地和物流大通道，同心同德，迎难而上，共同谱写嘉鱼经济社会发展新篇章！</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><br />\r\n&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('133','9','嘉鱼政务网编辑','嘉鱼政务网','<p align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><strong><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&mdash;&mdash;2011</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">月</span></strong><strong><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">日在县第十六届人民代表大会第七次会议上</span></strong><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">县长</span></strong><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> </span></strong><strong><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">夏福卿</span></strong><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">现在，我代表县人民政府向大会作政府工作报告，请连同《嘉鱼县经济和社会发展第十二个五年规划纲要（草案）》一并审议，并请县政协委员和其他列席人员提出意见。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年及</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">时期经济社会发展回顾</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，在市委、市政府和县委的正确领导下，在县人大、县政协的监督支持下，县政府坚持以邓小平理论和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三个代表</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实科学发展观，团结带领广大干部群众，同心协力，迎难而上，开拓进取，全县经济社会保持了良好的发展势头。据初步统计，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年全县完成生产总值</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">83.3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，按可比价格计算增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">18.0%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；完成规模工业增加值</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">50.94</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，按可比价格计算增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">33.0%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；财政总收入达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.71</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">34.5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，其中地方一般预算收入完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.95</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">34.5%;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">农民人均纯收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6675</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，比上年净增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">834</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元；全县万元</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">GDP</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">能耗同比下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5.4%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，二氧化硫和化学需氧量分别超减排计划任务的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">185.3%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">11.74%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，按期完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">规划节能减排目标。县域经济实力位居全市前列。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（一）农业经济逆势上扬，农业强县亮点纷呈。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年夏季，我县遭受了历史罕见的特大洪涝灾害。面对灾情，我们不等不靠，全力开展抗灾救灾和灾后重建工作，抗灾夺丰收取得全面胜利，工作经验在全省推广；自筹、整合资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元，开工建设各类水利工程</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">余处，完成土方</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">180</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万方，农业抗灾能力明显增强。大力推进农业标准化生产，积极创建</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全省蔬菜产业化示范县</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，兴办水产标准化健康养殖示范基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、畜牧标准化养殖示范基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，新认证无公害畜禽品牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">续展认证绿色食品蔬菜品牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">稻花香米</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">通过绿色食品品牌认证，统一注册</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">嘉鱼蔬菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">地理标识商标，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">洲湾鱼圆</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">被评为湖北省著名商标。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，全县农林牧渔业总产值达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">38.98</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12.0%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。新农村建设步伐加快，重点实施了官桥村、净堡村</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">迁村腾地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">整村推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项目建设，官桥村新建油茶基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亩，官桥村新社区一期工程全面启动。我县先后被授予全省首批十大农产品出口生产示范基地、全省农田水利建设先进单位和全省防汛抗洪先进集体等荣誉称号。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（二）工业经济生机勃勃，工业大县蒸蒸日上。始终把工业经济放在突出位置，坚持走新型工业化道路。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一区多园</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">建设成效显著，经济开发区优势凸显，规模企业发展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">60</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，经济总量占全县规模工业的比重接近</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">70%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；镇级工业园健康发展，潘家湾畈湖工业园被确定为市级化工园区，签订合同企业达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">31</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。固定资产投资强劲增长，全社会固定资产投资完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">76.97</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比上年增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">63.7%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。骨干企业数量进一步增加，全年新增规模工业企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，累计达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">150</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全年新建成投产项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">29</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，其中投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（三）旅游经济方兴未艾，旅游新县风生水起。高标准、高起点编制了《嘉鱼县旅游发展总体规划》，出台了《关于加快推进旅游新县建设的意见》；深入挖掘三国文化，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元兴建的二乔公园即将开园；旅游配套基础设施建设步伐加快，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1150</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的三湖桥及配套灯饰工程和投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">960</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的大崇山沿湖路相继建成，启动了一期投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2300</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的环梅懈湖景观带建设；旅游宣传推介氛围浓厚，目前洽谈的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个项目投资均过亿元，山湖温泉成功晋级国家</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4A</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">级景区，山湖温泉酒店顺利通过四星级旅游饭店评审。此外，我们不断提高旅游服务水平，大力规范旅游市场秩序，着力营造良好的旅游环境，带动了酒店、娱乐、商贸、金融及其他生产、生活性服务业的发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（四）基础设施日新月异，临港新城快速崛起。以建设临港新城为契机，加快出口通道建设和沿江资源开发。全面完成了嘉鱼至赤壁、嘉鱼至泉口两条出口路改造，陆口大桥主体工程已经完成，武嘉一级公路除余码头大桥外，其余路段已全线贯通；咸潘一级公路已进入开工前期准备阶段，嘉鱼长江大桥及外环高速项目已经省政府同意，由省交通运输厅高速公路管理局作为项目业主投资建设；潘家湾核电重件码头建设进展顺利。城区基础设施建设进程加快，筹资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元改造城区供水管网，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1685</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万元改造南门湖变电站，提升了城区公共服务设施保障能力。认真开展省级卫生县城和省级文明县城创建活动，人居环境进一步改善。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（五）改革开放与时俱进，开放嘉鱼稳步前行。政府机构改革稳妥推进，共取消、下放职责</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">11</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项，增加职责</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项，加强职责</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">58</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项，梳理并明确部门间职责分工</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项。改革后，部门内设机构减少</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，精简比例</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10.2%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，部门领导职数减少</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">56</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，精简比例</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">36.6%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，政府组织机构得到优化。招商引资成效显著，全年累计新签合同项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">71</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，实际到位资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">32.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，居全市之首，成功引进中国</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">强企业武烟集团。对外贸易大幅增长，据初步统计，全年外贸进出口达</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">926</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万美元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">281%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。财税金融对经济的支撑明显增强，金融部门不断扩大贷款投放规模和范围，有效服务了实体经济发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（六）社会事业齐头并进，和谐嘉鱼共建共享。社会保障体系不断健全，全县新增城镇就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5469</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，实现创业就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">590</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人；社会保险扩面新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7235</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，社会保险覆盖总人数达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">19</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人次；农村新型合作医疗参合人数达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25.1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人，参合率</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">97.4%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1200</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元完成了县福利院改扩建工程，标准堪称全省一流；一、二期廉租房均已投入使用，三期廉租房正在进行基础施工，全年共对</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2839</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">户困难家庭发放廉租住房补贴款</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">596</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。科教文卫事业全面进步，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">科技支撑服务行动</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">有效开展；农村办学条件进一步改善；镇综合文化站、新农村体育场地、农家书屋、文化信息资源共享工程等文化设施网络进一步健全；县人民医院迁建工程加快推进；创新计划生育利益导向机制，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">南嘉惠民计生阳光行动</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">深入开展；第六次人口普查工作顺利实施。信访维稳成效显著，畅通信访渠道，规范信访秩序，依法妥善解决了一批信访积案、难案和缠访案件；投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元完成平安城市视频监控系统建设，组织开展了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">打黑除恶</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">、命案攻坚、治爆缉枪、打击盗窃犯罪等专项行动，保持了全县的安定稳定。同时，民族宗教、外事、老龄、残疾人、防灾减灾等工作继续得到加强，审计、物价、工商、技术监督、统计、扶贫、档案方志、妇女儿童等工作也都取得了新成绩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">八件实事基本完成：一是投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元实施了城区供水管网改造，有效改善了城区供水状况；同时，解决了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.86</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万农村人口安全饮水问题。二是全年新增就业岗位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5217</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，转移农民工就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4560</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人。三是武嘉一级公路除余码头大桥外，其余路段已全线贯通；陆口大桥主体工程已经完成。四是总投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的二乔公园即将开园。五是嘉鱼大道已完成征地，拆迁完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">50%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，土方工程完成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">60%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。六是拟投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5307.4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的三湖连江景观带，一期工程已完成投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2300</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。七是樱花路南段延伸工程已完成部分征地。八是全年拆除违法建筑面积约</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">平方米，违建现象得到有效遏制。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">各位代表，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2010</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年各项工作任务的顺利完成，为</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">划上了圆满句号。五年来，全县上下坚持聚精会神搞建设，一心一意谋发展，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">规划确定的主要目标任务提前完成，全县经济社会发展取得新的重大成就。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，是我县经济总量不断增加，综合实力显著增强的五年。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">期末与</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">期末相比，生产总值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍，规模工业增加值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍，地方一般预算收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.22</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍，人均生产总值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍，城镇居民人均可支配收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">57.8%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，农民人均纯收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">97.4%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，全县金融机构存款余额增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.7</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍，贷款余额增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">倍。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，是我县基础设施不断完善，城乡面貌发生巨大变化的五年。全社会固定资产投资累计达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">190</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，比</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">规划目标翻了近一番，是</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍。累计改造新建通村公路里程</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">968</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里，完成省际出口公路</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">41</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里、县乡公路改造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">110</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里；完成渡口改造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">40</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">处、码头</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">座、五级站</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个。整治堤防长度</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">22.2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里，新增工程节水灌溉面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.09</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，有效灌溉面积达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28.49</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，除险加固小型水库</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">座，更新改造大型泵站</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">处、中型泵站</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">处，解决</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10.67</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万农村人口安全饮水问题。实施了城乡电网、通信网、有线电视网改造升级，全社会用电量由</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.01</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿千瓦时增加到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6.08 </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿千瓦时。县城区面积扩展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">平方公里，公共绿地面积达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">19.78</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万平方米，全县城镇化率由</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">36%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">52%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。新农村规划建设有效推进，分批改造完成新农村示范点</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">29</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，全县农村沼气池达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">13750</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">口。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，是我县改革开放深入推进，发展活力进一步增强的五年。政府统一采购、国库集中收付、行政事业性收费收支两条线管理等制度进一步完善；信用担保公司、城镇建设投资有限公司成功组建，成立了吴江村镇银行，企业融资难题得到有效缓解。土地收储中心正式运营，实行了土地出让招拍挂制度，集体林权制度改革顺利完成，集体土地市场流转试点和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">迁村腾地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">试点有序开展，基础设施建设和重点项目建设的用地需求得到了有效保障。招商引资力度持续加大，共引进项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">275</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，到位资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">82.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，是</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5.15</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">倍；其中投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">53</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，完成固定资产投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">54.8</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，是我县各项社会事业繁荣发展、人民群众得到较多实惠的五年。五年新增校舍</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7.6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万平方米，净增耕地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5828</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩；增加就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.86</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人，农村劳动力转移就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3.87</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人；城镇低保标准由每月</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">110</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">210</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，农村特困户救助标准由每人每月</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"> 55</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元。五年来，群众生活水平有了很大提高，城镇居民人均可支配收入由</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8945</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">13439</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，农民人均纯收入由</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3376</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元提高到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6675</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">元，人民生活正在向全面小康迈进。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，是我县行政效能不断提升、政府自身建设水平显著提高的五年。坚持把转变政府职能作为做好各项工作的基本途径，更加注重社会管理和公共服务，努力建设群众满意的服务型政府。积极推进政府绩效管理，健全应急救援和防灾减灾体系，完善信息公开、承诺服务和责任追究等制度，建立健全预防和惩治腐败长效机制，树立起了良好的政府形象和务实高效的行政新风。电子政务建设进程加快，行政服务中心正式挂牌运行，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">普法及依法治县工作取得新成绩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表，五年的历程极不平凡。这五年，是改革处于攻坚阶段、发展任务十分艰巨的五年，是我们战胜冰冻雨雪及特大洪涝等自然灾害挑战、积极有效应对国际金融危机不利影响的五年，是国家强化宏观调控、区域竞争异常激烈的五年。五年来，全县上下干事创业的氛围更加浓厚，加快发展的热情空前高涨，先后荣获全国食品安全示范县、全国平安县、全国绿化模范县、全省工业经济先进县、全省农民增收先进县、全省节能减排创新县、全省最佳金融信用县、全省蔬菜大县以及省级文明县城、省级园林城市、省级卫生县城等多项荣誉称号。今天的嘉鱼，经济健康发展，社会和谐稳定，人民安居乐业，以崭新的面貌站在了新的历史起点上。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">各位代表</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">五年的发展振奋人心，取得的成绩来之不易，这是在市委、市政府和县委的正确领导下，聚全民之智建农业强县、举全县之力建工业大县、开全域之源建旅游新县、借新港平台建临港新城的结果，是全县干部群众心齐气顺、风正劲足的结果，是历届县委、县政府奠定良好基础的结果，是县人大和县政协监督支持的结果。在此，我谨代表县人民政府，向全县广大干部群众，向各位人大代表、政协委员，向全县离退休老领导、老同志，向全体武警战士、消防官兵和政法干警，向所有关心支持嘉鱼发展的社会各界朋友，表示衷心的感谢，并致以崇高的敬意！</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">在充分肯定成绩的同时，我们也清醒地看到，当前全县经济社会发展还存在一些困难和问题。一是经济总量仍然偏小，综合竞争力还不够强，县域经济缺乏大的企业、项目和产业集群支撑；二是农业产业化程度不高，农产品附加值偏低；三是现代服务业发展不够，旅游开发水平有待进一步提高。这些问题，我们将在今后的工作中高度重视，采取切实有效的措施，认真加以解决。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">二、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">时期经济社会发展目标和主要措施</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">时期，是推进嘉鱼经济社会科学发展的关键时期，是加快转变发展方式的攻坚时期。根据县委十二届五次全会精神，县政府制定了《嘉鱼县经济和社会发展第十二个五年规划纲要（草案）》。《纲要（草案）》经本次大会审议通过后，我们将认真组织实施。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，中央促进中部地区崛起战略、扩大内需政策的深入实施，省</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两圈一带</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">、长江经济带新一轮开放开发、武汉新港和咸宁鄂南经济强市战略的纵深推进，以及国际国内资本、产业加速转移等，为我县经济社会发展带来千载难逢的大好机遇。时不我待，我们必须牢牢把握重要战略机遇期，攻坚克难，砥砺奋进，全力推进经济社会发展实现新突破、成就新跨越。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">时期，全县经济社会发展的指导思想是：坚持高举中国特色社会主义伟大旗帜，以邓小平理论和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三个代表</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实科学发展观和党的十七大、十七届五中全会精神，积极适应发展新形势，抢抓发展新机遇，顺应群众新期盼，以科学发展为主题，以加快转变经济发展方式为主线，深化改革开放，注重改善民生，着力推进农业强县、工业大县、旅游新县和临港新城建设，促进经济长期平稳较快发展和社会和谐稳定，实现财政收入和群众收入的新增长、强县与富民的新跨越，开创全县经济社会发展新局面，为全面建成小康嘉鱼打下具有决定性意义的基础。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">今后五年，全县经济社会发展的主要目标是：到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2015</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，全县生产总值达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">200</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，年均递增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">18.5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；三次产业结构调整为</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12.5:47.5:40</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；财政总收入达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，地方一般预算收入达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，年均分别增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">23.5%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；全县规模工业增加值达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">90</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，年均递增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；全社会固定资产投资达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">240</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿，年均增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25.6%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；城镇居民人均可支配收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">23500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，农民人均纯收入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元，年均分别增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">12%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">13.5%;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全县万元</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">GDP</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">综合能耗累计下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，主要污染物排放总量下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">为实现这些目标，《纲要（草案）》提出了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">时期我县经济社会发展的主要任务和措施：</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一是大力发展农业农村经济，推进全县新农村建设。围绕蔬菜、水产两大特色产业，进一步调整种养结构，优化农业产业布局，大力实施优质粮油、蔬菜板块、水产板块、林特板块、畜禽养殖等五大基地板块建设。完善农业标准化生产体系，加快农业产业化进程；继续推进绿色食品认证，推动农产品贴牌销售；着力培育壮大农产品加工企业，鼓励发展各类农民协会组织；加强农产品流通体系建设，繁荣武嘉公路沿线蔬菜交易市场。严格落实各级各类强农惠农政策；鼓励发展新型农村经济；完善农村基础设施和公共服务设施；建立完善促进城乡一体化发展的体制机制，加快小城镇建设步伐；继续推进农村社会事业建设，构建布局合理、配置均衡的公共服务体系。继续加快新农村建设，做好新农村建设推广示范，重点抓好官桥村、四邑村、净堡村整村推进建设项目。到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2015</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年，建成全省农业强县、全国蔬菜大县，在全省新农村建设中发挥表率作用。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">二是深入实施兴工强县战略，加快工业化进程。加快产业结构优化升级，推进轻纺、冶金、石化、建材、装备制造等传统产业集群式发展，大力发展高新技术产业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">, </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">全面提升工业经济整体竞争力。加快工业园区建设，提高省级嘉鱼经济开发区的承载力和竞争力，加强对镇级工业园规划建设的指导与扶持，构建多层次的工业经济板块和增长极。加大招商引资力度，着力引进技术新、规模大、前景好的大项目。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三是积极培育多元化市场主体，促进三产业健康发展。树立全域旅游理念，以</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">诗经中国，水墨嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">为主题，高标准整体投资开发县域旅游资源，逐年恢复历史文化古迹，同时加强旅游联合推介，发展区域旅游，打响嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">鄂南明珠、临港新城</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">品牌。投资建设潘家湾鄂南沿江物流聚集园区，完善现代商贸物流基地设施平台和公共商贸物流服务信息平台，构筑全方位物流配送服务网络，同时着力加强沿江物流载体建设，扶持壮大现代商贸物流企业。加快发展财税金融保险业，坚持</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">生财、聚财、理财</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">并举，促进财政与经济协调发展；坚持打造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">诚信嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">，加快各类金融机构的引进和发展，积极培育资本市场，缓解经济发展资金困难；积极开拓新型保险业务，加快开辟农村保险市场。整顿规范房地产市场秩序，促进房地产业健康发展。此外，还要大力发展邮政信息服务业、社区中介服务业等产业，促进第三产业发展迈上新的台阶。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四是加强城乡基础设施建设，改善优化发展环境。进一步完善陆路水路交通体系，重点建设嘉鱼长江大桥及外环高速、武嘉高速和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">条一级公路，争取将咸潘货运铁路、江南沿江铁路、环港城际铁路项目纳入省规划；加快石矶头港区、鱼岳港区、潘家湾港区各类码头的建设与改造。进一步加强水利工程建设，实施三湖连江、渗子湖灌区续建配套与节水改造工程，大力推进农村安全饮水、流域生态修复、水源地综合治理、水利血防等工程建设，加快实施以长江堤防险段综合整治、沿江涵闸除险改造、中小型水库和内湖围堤整险加固为主的防洪工程建设。优化能源生产结构，加快推进洲湾石油天然气钻探开发，积极开发利用各种新能源，促进全县能源消费结构多元化。加强城市建设专项规划的修编工作，统筹市政公用基础设施布局；着力完善城区道路、管网和公共绿地以及城市环境卫生基础设施，争创国家级文明城市和卫生城市。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五是推进体制机制创新，进一步扩大对外开放。深入推进经济体制改革，重点实施资源性产品价格和环保收费、收入分配、财税金融、土地管理和农村经济等领域或环节的改革。全面深化行政体制改革，强化政府公共服务职能，建立基本公共服务均等化体制机制，重点实施国有资产管理、行政审批、招投标管理、医药卫生、教育、文化、户籍以及事业单位等领域或环节的改革，统筹推进县内各镇协调发展，完善招商引资协调机制和利益分享机制。进一步开展对外交流与合作，提高利用外资的质量和水平，扩大外贸出口创汇，同时争取商检、海关在嘉鱼设立分支机构，加快</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大通关</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">进程。推进区域经济协作发展，以武汉城市圈、武汉新港和鄂南经济强市建设为纽带，全方位、多层次开展区域合作，促进劳动力、资本、技术等生产要素的自由流动，推动嘉鱼进一步开放开发。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">六是统筹社会事业发展，着力构建和谐嘉鱼。千方百计扩大就业，合理调节收入分配，不断健全和完善社会保障体系。促进各级各类教育、卫生、计生事业健康发展，进一步提高城乡教育质量、卫生水平、人口素质。鼓励发展公益性文体事业和经营性文化产业，着力丰富人民群众精神生活。加快推进科技进步，提高经济增长内生动力。全力推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两型</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">社会建设，促进经济效益、社会效益与生态效益相协调。进一步加强民主法制建设，建立健全安全体系，维护社会和谐稳定。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">此外，我们还要进一步做好民族宗教、外事工作，努力推进人事、统计、物价、工商、审计、技术监督、档案、史志、保密、扶贫和人防等事业，进一步关心和支持妇女、儿童、老龄、残疾人、慈善等事业发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三、扎实做好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年各项工作，努力实现</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">良好开局</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年是实施</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">规划的开局之年，也是我县抢抓机遇、加快发展的关键之年。做好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年政府工作，责任重大，意义深远。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年政府工作的指导思想是：坚持以邓小平理论和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三个代表</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实党的十七大和十七届四中、五中全会精神，以科学发展为主题，以加快转变经济发展方式为主线，更加注重改革创新、城乡统筹和改善民生，加快推进县域经济社会跨越式发展，为早日建成鄂南明珠、临港新城打下坚实的基础。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，全县经济社会发展总体目标是：努力实现</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一确保、双百亿、三领先</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">目标：即确保实现县域经济综合实力在全省排序中进位，生产总值和全社会固定资产投资分别突破</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，工业增加值、地方一般预算收入、农民人均纯收入增幅在全市各县市区位居领先位置。同时，全社会消费品零售总额增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，实际利用外资增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，外贸出口增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">40%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，万元</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">GDP</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">综合能耗下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个百分点，出生人口性别比下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个百分点，城镇居民人均可支配收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，城镇新增就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，五项保险新增扩面</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，人口自然增长率控制在</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6&permil;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以内，城镇人口登记失业率控制在</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以内，森林覆盖率达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">28%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，城镇化水平达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">56%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。实现今年的目标，要着力抓好以下几个方面的工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（一）注重高效发展，着力改善农业农村面貌。强化农田水利基础设施建设，加快农业信息化步伐，推进农业现代化进程，加快新农村建设，努力实现农业增效、农民增收、农村发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快农田水利基本建设。围绕提高农业抗灾能力，加大水利体制改革，切实激发镇村维护水利设施热情，做好全县水利普查工作，坚持应急与谋远相结合，科学制定建设规划，掀起新一轮农田水利建设高潮。实施好东西湖围堤、民堤民垸整险加固和长江干堤抛石护岸工程，搞好三湖连江水库灌区（潘家湾和洲湾段）续建配套与节水改造项目，推进幸福河、马鞍河、金水河流域治理、陆水灌区（嘉鱼片）项目建设，完成虎山、神塘小型水库除险加固，继续实施农村安全饮水工程，抓好中小泵站的维修与更新改造。全面实施农村供水管网改造和电网改造升级，提高农业抗御自然灾害能力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">着力发展现代高效农业。围绕蔬菜、水产和林特经济，大力发展设施农业，强化基地板块建设，在武嘉沿线新建或扩建蔬菜大棚</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩，全面完成大禾公司</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩设施农业基地建设，全年新增设施蔬菜面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩，新增油茶基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亩。大力推广水产健康养殖，发展休闲渔业，在沿湖、沿路、沿山建立配套垂钓场所，建成休闲渔业场所</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家以上。推行畜牧业规模养殖、生态养殖和标准化养殖，加快畜牧小区建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">提升农业产业化水平。坚持以工业化理念谋划农业发展，加强农产品质量安全和标准化生产，依托蔬菜、水产特色资源优势，加快渡普农产品加工产业园建设，着力打造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个集科研、示范、观光于一体的农业科技园。加大龙头企业的培植力度，全年新培植省级龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，市级龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，培育市级以上休闲观光农业示范单位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。大力推行</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">嘉鱼蔬菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">贴标上市销售，强化农产品加工转化与出口创汇，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年农产品加工转化率提高</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，农产品出口创汇</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万美元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加大新农村建设力度。坚持示范先行、典型带动，搞好官桥八组支持官桥村、联乐集团支持四邑村和湖北净宝农业开发公司支持净堡村等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">迁村腾地、产业先行、整村推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">新农村建设示范点建设。积极扩大示范成果，选择</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3-5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个基础条件较好的村开展迁村腾地建设试点，引导农民向中心村集中。坚持开展农村</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一建三改</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">基础工程建设，深入开展示范点环境整治，巩固新农村示范村建设成果。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（二）注重集聚发展，着力提升工业支撑能力。强化工业主导地位，加快工业大县建设，提升工业经济发展水平。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快一区多园建设。完善园区基础设施配套，加快开发区新征土地平整，完成园区一路、二路延伸工程及嘉鱼大道建设，真正形成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两纵两横</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的园区新框架。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，开发区新增规模企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，占规模企业的比重达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">75%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，入库税收达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元。加大对镇级工业园规划建设的扶持，推进镇级工业园基础设施建设，搭建企业发展良好平台。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，各镇工业园建设要有明显成效，潘家湾畈湖工业园新建成投产项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，鱼岳工业园新建成投产项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，洲湾工业园三木化工项目年底前要建成投产，其他镇工业园新建成投产项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个以上。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">做大做强优势产业。加快工业经济发展方式转变和结构优化升级，尽快形成一批新的经济增长亮点。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，上海华亿通橡胶产业园项目、洁丽雅产业基地项目、武汉永幸管业建材生产项目等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个已签约投资过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元重点项目，力争在上半年全面开工建设；中能锂电一期、嘉能热电迁建、联创食品等项目要在上半年投产；比伦纸业、禾丰湿纸巾、盛宇染织扩建、金嘉木业二期、武汉新联大、金桦实业二期等项目要在年底前建成。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，全县年税收过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元企业发展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家、过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元企业发展到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，规模工业入库税收新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万元。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加大招商引资力度。抢抓沿海地区产业转移、武汉城市圈建设、武汉新港建设机遇，落实招商引资优惠政策和奖励机制，积极创新招商引资方式方法，大力引进关联度高、附加值高的矿产资源开发、精细化工、大型制造和高新技术产业项目，延伸产业链，促进产业集群发展。</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2011</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年，全县新签合同项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">50</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，其中投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，力争新引进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家中国</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">强企业，努力在引进世界</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">强企业上实现突破。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">着力转变发展方式。进一步发挥市场作用，健全激励和约束机制，增强企业节能减排内生动力，鼓励发展循环经济和低碳经济，支持发展环保产业，突出抓好重点工程和重点领域的节能减排，加快淘汰落后产能，强化企业技术创新的主体地位，提高自主创新能力。全年新发展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家高新技术企业，完成节能减排降耗目标任务，努力实现绿色增长。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（三）注重均衡发展，着力培育壮大第三产业。树立全域旅游理念，以资源为依托，以文化为纽带，着力打造鄂南明珠、临港新城旅游品牌，推进服务业优化升级。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快发展旅游产业。挖掘文化内涵，整合诗经文化、温泉文化、三国文化、南宋文化等文化资源，打造具有地域特色的文化旅游品牌。突出水乡特色，积极引进海航集团高标准开发三湖连江、牛头山景区资源，力争启动</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个旅游项目。启动主坝路景点建设，完成三湖桥至白湖桥滨湖景观带工程，规划启动三湖连江桃花岛景点建设。大力发展农业观光旅游，依托蔬菜、水产特色产业，结合新农村建设，扶持在干道沿线发展一批高档次的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">农家乐</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">和庭园经济，积极推动官桥等湖北旅游名镇、名村配套建设。加强与周边县市在三国资源和温泉资源开发利用上的合作，形成、壮大区域旅游品牌，提高整体竞争力。突出优质服务理念，加强与高等院校合作，对旅游从业人员进行实用性强的各种形式的培训，提高服务质量，提升游客满意度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力发展现代服务业。加快编制全县商业网点规划，合理布局商业网点，大力发展连锁经营、特许经营等新型经营方式，逐步形成大市场、大流通格局。加大</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万村千乡</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">农家店建设力度，加快推进农贸市场改造升级，进一步做好家电下乡工作。强化市场秩序整治，重点加强蔬菜、建材、小商品批发等市场管理。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">鼓励发展文体事业。推进文化产业发展，加快公共文体设施、文化遗产、文化市场建设管理，规划建设县文体会展中心。加强对本土文化资源的搜集、整理，激励创作人员多出地方特色浓厚、艺术性强、群众喜闻乐见的本土文化艺术作品，满足人民群众精神文化需求。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">强化财税金融服务功能。提高财政运行质量，实施新的县镇财政体制，合理确定分成基数，充分调动各镇发展经济的积极性。巩固支柱财源、壮大新兴财源、培育后续财源，力争全年实现土地出让收益</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，确保重点工程项目、重大民生项目资金需求。改善金融服务环境，继续巩固</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">最佳金融信用县</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">创建成果，提高金融服务经济社会发展能力。加强银企合作，组织银企洽谈会，引导金融机构加大信贷投放。发挥中小企业贷款担保公司的作用，解决企业融资难的问题。依托城镇建设投资公司平台，深化与各商业银行的合作，争取更多的国家政策性贷款和中长期贷款。加强金融产品创新，筹建小额贷款公司，推进农村合作银行股份制改革，引导吴江村镇银行做大做强，力争全年新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家小额贷款公司和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家农村资金互助社。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（四）注重统筹发展，着力推进临港新城建设。抢抓武汉城市圈、武汉新港建设机遇，加快推进临港新城建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快交通基础设施建设。重点做好嘉鱼长江大桥及接线工程和咸潘一级公路开工前的准备工作。加快陆口大桥建设，确保今年完成桥面工程；做好武汉至嘉鱼沿江高速通道项目前期准备工作，全力争取将嘉鱼至赤壁古战场一级路纳入省规划，力争在年底前开工建设；全年改造通村公路</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里以上。充分开发、利用好沿江资源，加大对接武汉新港建设，加快沿江开发步伐，按</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">吨级标准改造临江山综合码头、中港码头、洲码头，完成潘家湾重件码头、潘家湾深水码头二期工程建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快发展商贸物流园。发展现代物流业，抓好现代物流基地、物流产业园、配送中心网络建设；结合嘉鱼长江大桥建设，尽快启动潘家湾物流产业园项目。引进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家大型商贸集团或商展贸易中心进驻嘉鱼，投资建设物流及配送大市场，拓展园区产业物流配送功能。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">强化城市规划建设管理。完善城区基础设施建设，抓好沿湖景观带工程和樱花路南段延伸工程建设，加快推进发展大道外国语学校至双引桥段人行道铺装工程，实施凤凰路和岳公路翻修改造工程，完成城区污水处理厂配套管网建设。注重城市科学规划，编制综合农贸市场、专业建材市场、服装市场、小商品市场等专业性规划，搞好城市管理，加强对二乔公园、人民公园等公众休闲场所的管理，进一步强化城区道路交通、环境卫生管理力度。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">推进城乡一体化建设。积极稳妥推进城镇化，合理确定城镇功能定位、产业布局，创新土地使用机制，增强产业支撑。提升城镇管理水平，针对城乡违法违规建设，采取强有力措施，依法依规拆违控违，维护广大人民群众权益。高质量推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">32</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万亩农村土地整治项目，切实改善农村生产生活条件。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（五）注重普惠发展，着力促进社会和谐稳定。围绕建设和谐社会目标，着力保障和改善民生，推进基本公共服务均等化，使发展成果惠及更多的人民群众，进一步提升群众的安全感和幸福感。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">不断完善保障体系。推进城乡居民社会养老保险工作，扎实开展被征地农民基本生活保障即征即保工作，进一步扩大企业养老保险、城镇职工基本医疗保险、大病医疗保险救助覆盖面。完善小额贷款担保工作机制，扩大放贷规模，推进城镇新增劳动力就业和下岗失业人员再就业。逐步健全住房保障体系，完成廉租房三期工程建设。建立健全农村低保和养老保险制度，不断完善城乡困难群众大病医疗、城乡孤儿、农村五保、慈善捐赠等专业救助制度，巩固提高最低生活保障水平。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">协调发展社会事业。坚持教育优先发展，重视教育规划，统筹推进学前教育、义务教育、高中教育和职业教育协调发展，全力提高办学质量和办学水平。完善以企业为主体、产学研相结合的技术创新体系，力争新创中国名牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、湖北名牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1-2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个。更加重视卫生事业发展，完成县人民医院主体工程建设，积极探索县、镇、村三级医疗机构卫生服务管理新体制。突出抓好计生基层基础建设、计生队伍建设和出生人口性别比偏高整治，全力破解流动人口管理瓶颈，严格依法征收社会抚养费，有效控制政策外生育。巩固食品药品安全示范县创建成果，加强食品药品市场监管，保障群众饮食用药安全。继续做好人事、统计、物价、史志、档案、慈善、残疾人、民族宗教、外事、扶贫等工作，支持国防建设，抓好人民防空和民兵预备役工作，关心和支持妇女、儿童、老龄等事业。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">切实维护社会稳定。加快推进依法治县进程，全力开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">平安嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建设，加强社会治安综合治理和公安基层基础建设。健全司法援助网络，完善人民调解工作机制，筑牢农村稳定第一道防线。严格落实信访工作责任，坚持县级领导定期接访和信访例会制度，完善县、镇、村三级信访网络，切实保障群众合理诉求。高度重视并努力抓好消防、交通和生产安全工作，加大隐患排查力度，全力保障公共安全和社会稳定。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">着力做好十件实事。今年，我们要重点做好十件实事：一是完成廉租房三期工程建设。二是至少解决</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万农村人口安全饮水问题。三是全年城镇新增就业岗位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，转移农村劳动力就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人。四是进一步推进官桥村、净堡村整村推进新农村示范点建设。五是规划建设嘉鱼文体会展中心。六是完成县人民医院主体工程建设。七是完成经济开发区园区一路、二路路基工程。八是改造通村公路</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">公里以上。九是启动全县留守流动妇女儿童服务中心建设。十是启动嘉鱼长江大桥和咸潘一级公路建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（六）注重创新发展，着力推进政府自身建设。切实转变政府职能，强化服务意识、创新服务体制、改进服务方式，充分发挥行政服务中心便民窗口作用，认真开展政风行风民主评议活动，提高服务质量和效率。更加注重履行社会管理和公共服务职能，更加注重保障和改善民生，下大力气解决好群众反映突出的问题。加快电子政务建设，提高电子政务应用水平，发挥政府网站作用，努力为城乡居民提供更加方便快捷的公共服务。增强政府工作透明度和公信力，完善重大事项公示和听证制度，自觉接受人大的法律监督、政协的民主监督和社会的舆论监督，提高行政决策科学化、民主化水平。着力建设法治政府，规范行政权力，加大行政综合执法改革力度，加强行政执法队伍建设，深入推进行政执法责任制，建立健全过错追究制和评议考核制，进一步规范执法程序，提高执法水平和质量。积极推进惩治和预防腐败体系建设，加大财政资金和民生资金审计力度，切实加强廉政监察、执法监察、效能监察，促进政府工作人员廉洁从政，倾力打造为民、务实、清廉的整体形象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">各位代表，回顾</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十一五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，成就巨大，我们深受鼓舞；展望</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">十二五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; m